description: IuaProfile: Table containing parameters for configuring Intra-eNodeB User Activity (IUA) profiles in a 5G/4G network, specifying thresholds and timers for user inactivity and resource management.  Columns describe timestamp, location (Area_Name, CellId), profile identifiers (Id2, Id3, IuaProfileId), various IUA parameters (e.g., buffer size, inactivity timer, SINR thresholds), and data versioning information.
